{"tid":1478842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府人員協會呼籲政治中立嘅公務員參加817撐黑警撐政府集會！","createTime":"2019-08-16T16:19:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T09:35:00.000Z","uid":61788,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"04aed1dea2324c270abd56af3c21f48b491b01af","tid":1478842,"uid":61788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T16:19:27.000Z","msg":"啱啱個post漏咗放相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 重開<br />\n<br />\n話說我收到個政府人員協會嘅msg<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1mCzNR8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1mCzNR8.png&h=86aada78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n㩒入去就見到佢哋帶頭呼籲政治中立嘅公務員參加817 「反暴力 救香港」集會<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FHWAxmQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFHWAxmQ.png&h=f8cd672c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再㩒入去就有張google form<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X3jqUzT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX3jqUzT.png&h=90d718ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為咗令大會作出妥善嘅安排，我就如實報咗佢部門會有3000個人去<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/16/234031_87fce9c39caaac3f767c0e93962aea36.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F16%2F234031_87fce9c39caaac3f767c0e93962aea36.png&h=8a18c4be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實真係好on9，反政府就話要政治中立<br />\n而家又叫人去撐政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔知幾時入咗呢個會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.geahk.org.hk/email/20190816.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.geahk.org.hk%2Femail%2F20190816.html&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0YL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=801987bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.geahk.org.hk/email/20190816.html</a>"},{"pid":"ecdbbd9d7455852c5eab5a62f698